description: Welcome to our place, a place where you will find authentic Mexican and Puerto Rican dishes with unique flavors. We offer food with so much delicious flavor that you won’t be able to resist asking for more. We pride ourselves in offering unique delicious items at affordable prices all from our mobile unit. It’s a unique food experience that’s sure to please. If our food doesn't catch your attention our full-size kitchen just might wow you. We hope you enjoy our food as much as we enjoyed making it for you. Thank you for your patronage and please come back and visit us often.
name: El Chile Caliente
